<h3 class="about_title text-center">Paper Template and Formatting Requirements</h3>
</div>
<div class="col-12">
<div class="am2-content">
<p>We recommend that authors submit their papers using LaTeX, and have provided a LaTeX template for use in compiling technical papers.</p>
<ul>
<li>The recommended <a href="https://latex-project.org/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">LaTeX</a> author kit/template may be <a href="/assets/files/grcon2016.tar.gz">downloaded here</a>.</li>
<li>If you cannot use LaTeX, a <a href="https://www.libreoffice.org/discover/writer/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">LibreOffice Writer</a> template may be <a href="/assets/files/grcon_format_libreoffice.odt">downloaded here</a>&nbsp;as an alternative.</li>
</ul>
<p>Please carefully review the requirements before submission and use the template provided!</p>
<p>Papers submitted to the technocal proceedings must:</p>
<ul>
<li>Be 8 pages or less in length (excluding references).</li>
<li>Use the provided template format&nbsp;above.</li>
<li>Contain substantive technical contribution or tutorials.</li>
<li>Cite relevant reference material appropriately.</li>
<li>Not be previously published in another venue.</li>
</ul>
<p>Authors must agree to allow us to distribute their work under a <a href="https://arxiv.org/licenses/nonexclusive-distrib/1.0/license.html">non-exclusive license to distribute</a>.</p>
